# Keep Docker build context small. Build context = repo root.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/out
**/.turbo
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
**/.env*.local
**/*.tsbuildinfo
applications/dashboard-ui/sentinelgrid.db
applications/dashboard-ui/sentinelgrid.db-shm
applications/dashboard-ui/sentinelgrid.db-wal
docs/screenshots
docs/diagrams/*.png
docs/diagrams/*.svg
docs/presentation/*.pdf
.git
